name: Firat NFTs Collection
description:
Fırat keeps reigning as the most famous comics hero of Turkey since he
came into our lives in 2007. The cartoonish life of this kid, who has a
language and a world-view of his own, has glimpses of everybody's
childhood one way or the other. Fırat has an answer to every situation
he finds himself in. He suffers no traumas whatsoever. He never cries,
even if he falls. He finds joy in falling in a cool manner. He can
imagine block-buster features with rockets exploding and cars crashing
one another with a slipper or a triple socket. His only concern is to
grow up fast, when he finally does, he imagines he will be the coolest
person on the planet. Fırat has 5 published books up to now, each of
them a best seller. He now multiplies in NFT.
